{"tid":256791,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你手上正好有 Switch 跟八位堂（8Bitdo）手把的話，告訴你一個好消息","createTime":"2017-05-24T19:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T10:53:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2793ff18959f082606cc868cb0778f8be0c66811","tid":256791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/3b170cba4096695d5d55003e29abe22c/205304747/8bitdo-nintendo-switch-controller-2017-05-24-01-ed.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2F3b170cba4096695d5d55003e29abe22c%2F205304747%2F8bitdo-nintendo-switch-controller-2017-05-24-01-ed.jpeg&h=bb4c36f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果你手上正好有 Switch 跟八位堂（8Bitdo）手把的話，告訴你一個好消息，它們現在可以放到一起使用了。早些時候八位堂發佈了一版新的的韌體，為旗下的全線產品（包括有 NES30 Pro、FC30 Pro、NES30、Zero 和 N64 手把）通通加入了 Switch 支援。當然囉，像是震動、NFC、運動控制等 Joy-Con、Switch Pro 手把特有的功能，非原廠的配件還是沒法享受到。但就算是這樣，光靠復古的造型應該已經足夠吸引一大批人了吧。<br />\n<br />\n根據 Reddit 上部分玩家的回饋來看，更新之後用八位堂的手把玩 Switch 上的遊戲「十分流暢」。只是，很難講老任那邊會不會允許這樣的情況一直存在下去啊...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/7b7845a677cb3714dcb2c87a4e3443e6/205303318/8bitdo-nintendo-switch-controller-2017-05-24-02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2F7b7845a677cb3714dcb2c87a4e3443e6%2F205303318%2F8bitdo-nintendo-switch-controller-2017-05-24-02.jpg&h=72f9c2db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2d78ff0f1b1bfa1cf68703b59a6aaf42cd61af8","tid":256791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba7e0caedd2607a691d6f55c6047732094b2ce2","tid":256791,"uid":87820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"有拳皇玩？"},{"pid":"76cc1ea83acb52165ca28a09c7f967812930591a","tid":256791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc